{"tid":993921,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"燈神紀錄系列-01","createTime":"2019-01-24T09:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T09:49:12.000Z","uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d305b4457357ed3ac946422839006135045da0e8","tid":993921,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T09:43:12.000Z","msg":"睇住咁多巴打出post, 終於想出個post ， 分享下我好自豪的賭術！！<br />\n無睇錯標題，我係燈神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊解會咁講：買親波馬都輸9成，又戒唔到賭。<br />\n即使買賠率極低的波，亦都會輸。<br />\n前年輸5萬+，上年輸4萬+。<br />\n聖誕到而家一月中輸咗6-8k。<br />\n<br />\n出個post 記低自己點柒法，買一場輸一場，買兩場2穿1，總會輸1場。<br />\n<br />\n等陣出下舊飛留念下。<br />\n有興趣睇下，買我對家，或者避開我買的場次。<br />\n<br />\n1/24<br />\n得盃賽，全放棄買咁濟。<br />\n本身仲想買巴塞上盤/格流客勝，戶口無錢放棄咗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BSZQwJz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSZQwJz.png&h=3171fe8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"effc4c1d802464bb4bf2dfcbbe267313509f59a4","tid":993921,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T09:49:12.000Z","msg":"1/21 仆街祖記，明明次次入1-2球收工，點撚解入咁多球，屌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q9dhWbw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq9dhWbw.png&h=912485a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身想買伊巴，係最後時間，上盤不斷跌水，覺得鬼而作罷。"}]}